              NCA5 will assess current and future risks posed by climate change to each of NCA’s 10 regions, illustrated below.
            </p>
            <img alt="NCA5 Regions Map" class="regions-img" 
            src="https://www.globalchange.gov/sites/globalchange/files/NCA%20regions_sm.png">
            <div class="legend">
              <ul>
                <li>Legend: </li>
                <li>Item 1</li>
                <li>Item 2</li>
                <li>Item 3</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </section>
